import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import {Playground} from 'docz'
import Select from './Select'
import Box from './Box'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"select"}}>{`Select`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Box>
  <Select
    label="Please select an option"
    name="select"
    values={[\'Yes\', \'No\', \'Maybe\']}
    placeholder="Select"
    options={[\'Yes\', \'No\', \'Maybe\']}
  />
</Box>`} __scope={{props,Select,Box}}>
  <Box>
    <Select 
      label="Please select an option"
      name='select'
      values={['Yes','No', 'Maybe']}
      placeholder='Select'
      options={['Yes','No', 'Maybe']}/>
  </Box>
</Playground></MDXTag>
